## What does Rockerbox do best?

Before switching, acknowledge Rockerbox's genuine strengths:

| Strength | Why It Matters |
|----------|----------------|
| **Podcast attribution** | Best proxy methods available (vanity URLs, surveys, MMM) |
| **TV/OTT measurement** | Device graph, IP matching, model flexibility |
| **Direct mail tracking** | Promo codes, address matching |
| **Influencer attribution** | UTMs, codes, survey integration |
| **MMM included** | Econometric modeling alongside MTA |

**If podcasts or TV are major channels, Rockerbox is hard to replace.** Alternatives handle these channels less well.

